{"tid":1723633,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"幫屋企部大電視加多 NowTV 新聞台","createTime":"2019-11-15T08:44:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T01:16:58.000Z","uid":121636,"like":84,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"d260a9e1c34de76bdefc5dab02070e39e4c8db73","tid":1723633,"uid":121636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:44:52.000Z","msg":"如果你屋企無裝 NowTV，屋企人日日開 CCTVB 洗自己腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到底 NowTV 新聞台是不是只有訂戶才能享用的特權？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tecky.io/static/5dc906abe256dIMG_7058-e9f457670e3adf92fb6d793452c28a39.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftecky.io%2Fstatic%2F5dc906abe256dIMG_7058-e9f457670e3adf92fb6d793452c28a39.jpg&h=21a50cbc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然不是！其實網上早有 NowTV 新聞台直播，但仍然有不少人習慣看家裡的大電視 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，如果沒有安裝 NowTV 或有線電視，那麼新聞台的選擇就只有 83 台 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，即使知道以 HDMI 或 Chromecast 接駁電腦能夠看到其他頻道甚至 Facebook Live，繁複的設置也往往令人卻步。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今天，讓我們教大家把網上的 NowTV 新聞台 &amp; 直播台，無縫連接上電視，為自己、為家人，輕鬆添置多一個新聞台選擇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">材料需要：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tecky.io/static/5dc907a0b63fbIMG_9802-29bd1216f5ee3a090e946e66614d12d5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftecky.io%2Fstatic%2F5dc907a0b63fbIMG_9802-29bd1216f5ee3a090e946e66614d12d5.jpg&h=9641c4d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n．Raspberry Pi 第三代 Model A/B 或 Model B+ （第四代也可以，但需要配置 Mini-HDMI to HDMI 的接駁器）<br />\n．Raspberry 火牛（其他火牛也可以，不過若供電不穩，可能會出現「疾機」的情況）<br />\n．Raspberry 外殻（可買可唔買）<br />\n．8GB 或以上的 MicroSD Card<br />\n．HDMI 線<br />\n<br />\n以上材料的成本不超過 $500 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">軟件準備：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n因為時間關係，我們已經預先把軟件安裝好，並製成「懶人包」，成為一個可直接燒錄的系統映像檔 (zip, 1.2GB)：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/teckyio/nowpi/releases/download/v0.1.2/nowpi-0.1.2.img.zip\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fteckyio%2Fnowpi%2Freleases%2Fdownload%2Fv0.1.2%2Fnowpi-0.1.2.img.zip&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYbeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=e7f6154c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/teckyio/nowpi/releases/download/v0.1.2/nowpi-0.1.2.img.zip</a><br />\n<br />\n先把以上「映像檔」下載到你的電腦，把 MicroSD Card 插上，然後把映像檔燒錄至 MicroSD Card。<br />\n<br />\n應該怎樣燒錄？我們推薦使用 balenaEtcher (<a href=\"https://www.balena.io/etcher/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.balena.io%2Fetcher%2F&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYbeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=d2fabd25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.balena.io/etcher/</a>) 去燒錄，只需選擇下載好的映像檔和 MicroSD Card，輕鬆簡單便可完成。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tecky.io/static/5dc90989b8b6betcher-0b9a865ec6ba01c90d9547bef092da38.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftecky.io%2Fstatic%2F5dc90989b8b6betcher-0b9a865ec6ba01c90d9547bef092da38.png&h=07b63ef8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">設定 Wi-Fi：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">假若你的電視支援 HDMI-CEC （大部份電視都支援）</span>，直接把 MicroSD Card 插入 Raspberry Pi，接駁上電視和電源，按著畫面指示，用你的<strong>電視遙控</strong>設定 Wi-Fi，便大功告成！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tecky.io/static/5dc90bf4dc5e2IMG_9658-10b41fc809f4c9762fa8020976ffb605.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftecky.io%2Fstatic%2F5dc90bf4dc5e2IMG_9658-10b41fc809f4c9762fa8020976ffb605.jpg&h=16000638&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">更可以用 <strong>電視遙控</strong> 轉 直播台 和 新聞台</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://github.com/teckyio/nowpi/raw/master/hdmi-cec-sample.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fteckyio%2Fnowpi%2Fraw%2Fmaster%2Fhdmi-cec-sample.gif&h=88aab4e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">假若你的電視未能支援 HDMI-CEC ，</span>就要麻煩少少。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n先把 MicroSD Card 抽出再插回電腦，電腦會詢問是否需要格式化 MicroSD Card，可以按略過，然後會見到 MicroSD Card 的磁區，在這裡打開名為 <code>wpa_supplicant.conf</code> 的檔案，如果沒有這個檔案，亦可以新增這個檔案。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tecky.io/static/5dc90dde7c138Screen-Shot-2019-11-11-at-3.32.17-PM-cbb31b362e97c2bbb1522ef145c58a0e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftecky.io%2Fstatic%2F5dc90dde7c138Screen-Shot-2019-11-11-at-3.32.17-PM-cbb31b362e97c2bbb1522ef145c58a0e.png&h=a4b4b600&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後用 記事本 (Windows) 或 Visual Studio Code (Mac)，寫入以下資料：<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">country=HK\nctrl_interface=DIR=/var/run/wpa_supplicant GROUP=netdev\nupdate_config=1\n\nnetwork={\n    ssid=&quot;你的Wi-Fi名稱&quot;\n    psk=&quot;你的Wi-Fi密碼&quot;\n}</code></pre><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tecky.io/static/5dc9787621b9dScreen-Shot-2019-11-11-at-11.07.19-PM-44c6dddc431e895052a693065008cf04.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftecky.io%2Fstatic%2F5dc9787621b9dScreen-Shot-2019-11-11-at-11.07.19-PM-44c6dddc431e895052a693065008cf04.png&h=891e86bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n設定好之後，把 MicroSD Card 退出。<br />\n<br />\n接好 Raspberry Pi 和電視後，它便會自動連上相對應的 Wi-Fi 網絡。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">聽人講，就咁用人哋啲嘢唔安全喎！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n不怕！我們已經將 Source Code 放上 GitHub 開源，歡迎提出修正，甚至自行建立屬於自己的映像檔 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://github.com/teckyio/nowpi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgithub.com%2Fteckyio%2Fnowpi&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYbeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=25f00717\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://github.com/teckyio/nowpi</a>"},{"pid":"e6b29c0d3b73819163e66419e23a8174c49a425e","tid":1723633,"uid":249263,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:45:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">出門之前 rt like reply</span><br />\nTwitter組會keep住更新<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n㩒入👉<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYbeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=0843b168\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a><br />\n然後打 /task 攞任務<br />\n<br />\nSenator Scott 幫香港人出聲<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Rt + like </span><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/senrickscott/status/1195147582609252353?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenrickscott%2Fstatus%2F1195147582609252353%3Fs%3D21&d=DwP82Rd5Y8BeeioconDBYbeFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=992848e9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsenrickscott%2Fstatus%2F1195147582609252353%3Fs%3D21&h=37d03fec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/senrickscott/status/1195147582609252353?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"c7a3a96cb34dfc4f61e65108cd4ec2f2b93f66a8","tid":1723633,"uid":147916,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T08:46:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/67reh